Package: ffiec
Type: Package
Title: FFIEC Central Data Repository REST API Client
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Michael", "Thomas", email = "mthomas@ketchbrookanalytics.com",
           role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Ketchbrook Analytics", role = c("cph", "fnd"))
  )
Description: A client for the FFIEC (Federal Financial Institutions Examination Council)
    Central Data Repository REST API. Provides functions to retrieve filer data
    and other regulatory information using the httr2 package.
